; BIND reverse data file for empty rfc1918 zone

; DO NOT EDIT THIS FILE - it is used for multiple zones.
; Instead, copy it, edit named.conf, and use that copy.

$TTL    5
@       IN      SOA     rajoy.francisco.gonzalonazareno.org. francisco.gonzalonazareno.org. (
                              1         ; Serial
                         604800         ; Refresh
                          86400         ; Retry
                        2419200         ; Expire
                          86400 )       ; Negative Cache TTL

@       IN      NS      rajoy.francisco.gonzalonazareno.org.
$ORIGIN francisco.gonzalonazareno.org.
